the Fred Fish library CDs and on Aminet CDs.

 Qwk2Pkt may not appear on a BBS that charges for time.  Of course, this
includes so-called Premium rate (0891 etc) lines in the UK.

 Oh, one more thing:  Don't add any of those silly .displayme files please!

@ENDNODE
