@NODE History "History of Qwk2Pkt"

    Version 1.0 - 6.11.94

    ·   first version released


    Version 1.1 - 4.4.95

    ·   Note that my FidoNet and AmigaNet addresses have changed.  Please
        don't send mail to my old addresses as I wont ever see it.

    ·   New feature: Added the NOREQ switch.  If this is turned on, AmigaDOS
        requesters for Qwk2Pkt are turned off.  This is mainly useful for
        unattended machines.

    ·   Bug fix: Cleanup routine could have caused a crash (I'm surprised it
        worked at all :-)

    ·   Capitalization much smarter: "John G.Barrot", "Daniel Campion-Smith",
        "Steve O'Malley" etc. will now capitalize correctly.

    ·   Bug fix: command line parsing error would lead to memory loss.

    ·   New feature: Names like McGee will be properly capitalized if an
        entry is in ENV:Qwk2Pkt.names.  See the CN=CORRECTNAME/S switch for
        details.

    ·   Better Origin line detection.  Now works properly with more doors
        [may need more attention].


	Version 1.2 - 30.8.10

    ·   Re-released to Aminet but the source code is now included.

    ·   Contact addresses have been updated in this guide file.

@ENDNODE

